headline: Jacobs to Expand Backlog With Multi-Year Marselis Tunnel Project
summary: J to boost its infrastructure portfolio with Denmark's Tunnel project, driving backlog growth and long-term momentum.

headline: Jacobs to Deliver New York's Transformative Interborough Express Light Rail Project
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J), in joint venture with HDR, has been selected to provide engineering consultant services for the Metropolitan Transportation Authority's (MTA) Interborough Express (IBX) Light Rail Project – a new transit line connecting communities across Brooklyn and Queens, New York.
